\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li624\ri0\lin624\rin0\fi-624\f2\fs22\lang7177\f0\fs22\f8\fs20\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj [37]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls0\li624\ri0\lin624\rin0\fi-624\rtlch\af8\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af0\langfe255\hich\f2\fs22\lang7177\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch After raising the issue the merging parties and the Commission agreed that the undertaking could be made a condition of approval. This has obviated the need for us to make any further enquiry into the possibility of the merger increasing co-ordination post
 merger in the SVR market. The present condition will serve to ensure that Remgro adopts proper procedures to avoid information flow between the firms that may be potentially anticompetitive.}
